---
// Persistent bio/intro block in the content pane — renders on every page
// (Home/Blogs/Projects), with page-specific content below it.
---

<div class="pb-8 mb-12 border-b border-white/5">
  <div class="font-mono text-xs text-neutral-600 mb-2">$ cat bio.txt</div>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
    I'm a Senior Software Engineer based in Hyderabad, India, with 8 years in
    tech — mostly full-stack and integration work, with an eye on
    architecture next.
  </p>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed max-w-xl mt-4">
    Currently building at GE Vernova, learning Go on the side, and open to
    open-source or integration projects if the timing (and my laziness)
    allows. Right now that's bytes-of-me — this site.<span class="intro-cursor text-neutral-500">▋</span>
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .intro-cursor {
    display: inline-block;
    animation: intro-blink 1s steps(1) infinite;
  }
  @keyframes intro-blink {
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }
</style>
